Bit by Bit about linux (Redhat,Ubuntu,CentOS)
$tar
***************************************************************************
tar jcvf dir.tar.bz2 ./dir     //bzip2
tar jxvf dir.tar.bz2 ./dir     //bzip2

tar zcvf dir.tar.gz ./dir      //gzip
tar zxvf dir.tar.gz ./dir      //gzip
***************************************************************************
-k //for keep *.tar.bz2 for when uncompress
